{
  "id": "adv_event_2603_01_01",
  "title": "アンサー\nソング",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストバレンタインライブ　練習期間中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 1.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2200
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "明日の予定は……っと、バレンタインライブの\n打ち合わせが終われば二日間のお休みかぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.7333333254,
      "endTime": 12.193831944500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが空けてくれた二日間で\n絶対『この曲』を完成させないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3804984968,
      "endTime": 17.2828339498,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5387.1893802
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……コードとかメロディとか、難し過ぎる\nなんで作曲までやるって言っちゃったんだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4895003875,
      "endTime": 27.0895005782,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.2194991986
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "（私は初のソロライブツアーに向けて、ずっと新曲）\n（『With your songs』の準備をしていた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.2694991986,
      "endTime": 36.8399526517,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9297.106011699998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.0332861185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、お誕生日おめでとう。はい、これ\n『song for you』のアンサーソング",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0332861185,
      "endTime": 45.638025116899996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.8513584693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと過ごしたかけがえのない日々への感謝と\nこれからもステージで歌い続ける決意を込めた曲なの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.8513584693,
      "endTime": 53.6834219535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cemetery-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cemetery-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8967550199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞は出来たんだけど、メロディがまだで……\nでも、絶対に完成させるからもう少し待っててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8967550199,
      "endTime": 63.8115621488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "（アイドルとして成長した今、私なりの言葉で）\n（お姉ちゃんに曲を贈ろうと決めてから、数ヶ月）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9915626765,
      "endTime": 73.3114944697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんの誕生日に、なんとか歌詞は）\n（プレゼント出来たけど、曲の方は全然だなぁ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.511494279,
      "endTime": 81.75197069650001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "（今度のソロライブツアーには絶対に間に合わせないと）\n（いけないのに……焦れば焦るほどメロディが浮かばない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9386372488,
      "endTime": 91.7569134634,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_piano-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16461.3627512
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……お姉ちゃんはこんな時、どうしてたんだろう\nあら？　どこからかピアノの音が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9702467204,
      "endTime": 103.2000030518,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12763.089664700005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_piano-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12631.068261400003
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17629.756331400004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.3513149818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "すずの部屋から聞こえてくるみたい……\nすずー、忙しいところごめんね、入ってもいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.4013149818,
      "endTime": 114.6637201866,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16541.908914100004
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16628.74483270001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyodormcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyodormcorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.7803874573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あら、琴乃？　どうぞ遠慮せず、お入りくださいまし\nそれにしても、こんな時間にどうした――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.8303874573,
      "endTime": 126.203766211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.0196475409
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.3504308623
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "なっ！？　琴乃が着けているそのペンダントは\n麻奈様が雑誌で私物として紹介していた物では！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3504308623,
      "endTime": 134.3559357566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.5626025758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "え？　あぁ、うん。一応同じものかな。お姉ちゃんへの\nアンサーソングを作る時は、必ず着けるようにしてるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.5626025758,
      "endTime": 146.52119670730002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.7211967073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "って言っても、作曲の方は全然なんだけど\nすずも、ソロ曲を作ってるのよね？　どう？　順調？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.7211967073,
      "endTime": 157.6467526995,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.8600860519
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "歌詞が難航したので、私も順調……とは言い難いですわ\nスマホのピアノアプリで作曲を、と思ったのですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8600860519,
      "endTime": 170.1619180604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ピアノ自体、しばらく触っていなかったので、どうにも\nビビビーっとくるようなメロディが浮かばず……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0999994915,
      "endTime": 178.3637409847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 178.5523348414
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……昔、ピアノコンクールで賞を総なめにして\n『戦慄の旋律』と言われていた頃が恋しいですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 178.5523348414,
      "endTime": 189.6437891566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.8437889659
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono Nagase",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "その変な異名、すずのことだったの？\n小学校の頃に出たピアノの発表会で、噂になってたっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8437889659,
      "endTime": 200.4467369639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu Narumiya",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2603_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "変！？　わ、私なりに考えて名乗っていましたのよ\nでも、琴乃もピアノを習っていましたのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.4333419801,
      "endTime": 210.6806211473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.6334035162
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyosuzroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 210.7673431322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
